channel.title: Modern Warfare 2 trickshotting
channel.description: Hey guys, I don't know about you but I still play MW2 even though black ops has been out about a year now. I have a clan and we go online S&D and trickshot. I've been looking for more people to party up with so if you trickshot post back here and tell me your GT and we can go on together and trickshot <3
